WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:01.700
I used you.

2
00:00:01.700 --> 00:00:03.800
You're using me now

3
00:00:03.933 --> 00:00:05.200
And that's fair.

4
00:00:05.766 --> 00:00:07.000
You should know

5
00:00:07.266 --> 00:00:08.900
You're at a disadvantage.

6
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:11.566
And when you do that, you get nothing in return.

7
00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:13.866
I just hope Guoguo

8
00:00:13.866 --> 00:00:15.633
To grow up safe and happy

9
00:00:16.666 --> 00:00:18.266
Marriage and love

10
00:00:18.733 --> 00:00:20.966
It didn't belong to someone like me

11
00:00:22.133 --> 00:00:23.166
It's you

12
00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:25.400
No need for me

13
00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:27.500
Do something that consumes yourself

14
00:00:30.566 --> 00:00:33.400
Are you sure you want to be used by me?

15
00:00:33.966 --> 00:00:36.166
As long as Xiao Jiang never forgets

16
00:00:36.166 --> 00:00:38.800
What kind of person is Wang Yu?

17
00:00:40.266 --> 00:00:40.966
What do you mean?

18
00:00:40.966 --> 00:00:44.266
I don't know what abacus Mr. Jiang is playing in his heart

19
00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:46.900
But I don't think you're stupid enough

20
00:00:46.900 --> 00:00:49.566
Let Wang Yu's purpose be by your side

21
00:00:58.066 --> 00:01:00.866
You can use me to achieve your goals

22
00:01:01.333 --> 00:01:02.833
My only request

23
00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:05.333
I just hope that Wang Yu doesn't have the opportunity to treat Guoguo

24
00:01:05.333 --> 00:01:07.833
He's such a proud man

25
00:01:07.866 --> 00:01:10.000
He actually bowed his head in front of me

26
00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:15.233
In fact, I have already thought about what to do with Furong Yu

27
00:01:17.933 --> 00:01:19.000
Pardon me?

